reviews.review_text:
Best Audience At this point, I have so many soundboards that I'm just looking for audience recordings of memorable shows.

So just considering the downloadable, audience recordings of this show ... on 25-04-21 I judged this one to be the best.

My criteria was just to compare several spots in "Love the One Your With". I felt this one had better clarity without suppressing Lesh's bombs too much.

For me, that song's the reason to have this show: a decent show, a passable recording, and something unique.

Overall, it's not a stellar show. And the recordings are all on the weak side. But after that spring tour finished up ... the Stills shows were what everyone talked about.
